# GitHub Linguist overrides.
#
# `patches/` holds vendored third-party crates carrying their own
# upstream C/C++ sources (opus, webrtc-audio-processing), patched only
# where Alexandria needs them. They are not Alexandria's own code and
# should not count toward the repository's language statistics — without
# this, ~704 vendored C/C++ files render a Rust project as ~36% C.
patches/** linguist-vendored

# Compiled Plutus blueprints and Aiken build output are artifacts, not
# hand-written source. (Aiken itself is detected natively by Linguist;
# the validators under cardano/governance/validators are real source and
# are deliberately left alone here.)
**/plutus.json linguist-generated
cardano/governance/build/** linguist-generated
